fields.description:
On Droid Turbo, Titanium API returns Ti.Platform.displayCaps.density as `medium`.

Note: It has high resolution 1440 x 2560 pixels screen and high pixel density 565 ppi.

Test Case:

{{
{code:java}
Ti.API.info("density: " + Ti.Platform.displayCaps.density);
{code}
}}

1. Run code, should see 'density: xxxhigh'
